  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening older people&#x2019;s association representatives in disaster preparedness and coordinate at the national and local levels to ensure older people are included in emergency responses and increase their self-reliance.

Supporting the distribution of temporary shelter materials to vulnerable older Haitians.

Continue with networking, advocating for and supporting disaster risk reduction and shelter solutions

Radio broadcast announcements on community and national stations for the protection of older during disasters.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project facilitates older people&#x2019;s access to available emergency assistance and support such as food and NFIs to enable them to survive with dignity. Also, the project provides information, advice and advocacy to other providers to ensure emergency needs of older people are included in emergency distributions and services.</narrative>
